data.description: Discover the perfect blend of space, comfort, and style in this charming 3 true bedrooms and 4th room that is currently being used as an office, 2 bathroom home nestled in the heart of Crawfordville, FL. Spread over 1600 sq ft, this residence offers a seamless flow between functionality and relaxation. The welcoming atmosphere begins in the spacious living areas, designed for everyday living and entertaining, and extends into a convenient home office space, perfect for meeting the demands of work from home or organizing your personal affairs. The large yard calls for outdoor enjoyment, perhaps hosting lively gatherings, engaging in recreational activities, or cultivating a garden haven.  The master bedroom features a substantial closet space ready to accommodate your wardrobe and adjoining master bathroom. The screened-in back porch adds a delightful touch, offering a comfortable transition space between indoor coziness and the allure of the outdoors, where you can relish in the serenity of the neighborhood, enjoy meals, or engage in quiet reflection.
